 HarmonyOS Next 的用户在可以使用的应用程序方面将面临更少的选择...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/11/26/24306370/huawei-mate-70-pro-plus-android-google-harmonyos-next&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306370/huawei-mate-70-pro-plus-android-google-harmonyos-next" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/26/24306370/huawei-mate-70-pro-plus-android-google-harmonyos-next</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry></feed>